    "Some customers will be more sophisticated than others in their risk assessment.",
    "For instance, repeat purchasers may accurately know the risks, while first-time customers may not.",
    "With the introduction of AI-based products, many customers will be first-time customers.",
    "Thus, customers' knowledge of the risks of AI-based products will likely be limited. 17",
